<BlogPost
  title="How to Get Rid of Mosquitoes in Your Yard (What Actually Works) | The Life Insider"
  description="Most yard mosquito problems come from breeding sites you can remove for free. Here's the order of operations that works — and the popular 'solutions' that don't."
  h1="How to Get Rid of Mosquitoes in Your Yard"
  dateLabel="July 2026"
  dateISO="2026-07-18"
  readTime="8 min read"
  lede="Before you buy anything, know this: the mosquitoes bothering you were almost certainly born in your own yard, in water you could pour out in ten minutes. Fix the source first and every other method works dramatically better."
